{
  "stem": "24830.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't want to go back to-- to this life.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when I came out of the movie, somebody stole the wheel of my bicycle, [LAUGHS] to make me feel badder.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was very difficult to find bicycle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But of course, the underground give me another bicycle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there is much more, but-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] that I remember, yeah, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, what I want to say is the-- the priest, and the minister, and some people in the government were very helpful.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were doing false paper-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There is the man in charge of the Protestant, you know, the minister-- who is quite known.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think he is known in this country, too-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, I was his-- I was the one who come to see him.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he has his people for-- for-- like he has Jew, and he has other people for other thing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I will come.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he will give me, without explanation, he is giving me the picture.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he say, I need so many false paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Then I will-- and I didn't ask him anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he didn't ask me anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I will come back and-- and give him the false paper.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one thing-- they told you never fill out the paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I go to these people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Half of them were not even French.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't know to write well.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So then I fill the paper anyway.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So like I tell you, I always come a few minutes before or after the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one day, one day before-- before really, I was very involved.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was on the beach in Nice, and the German follow me, you know, and keep bothering me.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wanted to talk to me, everything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
